<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Springbank Hill</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The community is administered by the Springbank Hill Community Association, which is currently working to develop a community centre, programs and recreation facilities.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Springbank Hill is a short drive from Springbank Hill is Weaselhead, a great place to jog, hike and bike ride, popular for its scenery and wildlife.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">North of the community is Westside Recreation Centre, complete with a fitness centre, swimming pool and other facilities.</p>

